.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
5 different games are played: backgammon, snooker, mah-jongg, whist, domino
House: townhouse, futuristic, cape-cod, ranch-style, colonial
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: soccer, rowing, cycling, weightlifting, tennis
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: time-travel, comedy, horror, superhero, thriller
The people have 5 different jobs:  analyst, software-developer, videographer, chef, architect

1. the townhouse house is the person playing backgammon
2. the futuristic house is the analyst
3. the person watching time-travel movies is the person playing snooker
4. the cape-cod house is the person watching comedy movies
5. the person playing snooker is to the right of the person playing mah-jongg
6. the person who's sport is soccer is the architect
7. the person who's sport is rowing is the person playing whist
8. the person watching horror movies is in the middle
9. the ranch-style house is on the far left
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the software-developer
11. the person who's sport is rowing is to the left or right of the chef
12. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person watching superhero movies
13. the colonial house is the person who's sport is tennis
14. the ranch-style house is to the left or right of the person playing domino

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| House	|   ranch-style	|    cape-cod	|     townhouse	|    futuristic	|    colonial	|
| Game		|    whist	|      domino	|      backgammon	|     mah-jongg	|     snooker	|
| Movie-Genre	|     thriller	|      comedy	|      horror	| superhero	|     time-travel	|
| Sport		|     rowing	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| weightlifting	|   parliament	|
| Job		|     software-developer	|     chef	|     architect	|     analyst	|     videographer	|
